OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA fine
OL,6,Fevening with some late sunshine for
OL,7,Fmany. Patchy low cloud will form in
OL,8,Feastern and central areas with perhaps
OL,9,Fthe odd spot of rain by dawn.
OL,10,FRemaining clear further west where it
OL,11,Fwill be another warm night.
OL,12,
OL,13,CMonday:FLow cloud clearing through the
OL,14,Fmorning with many areas dry and sunny.
OL,15,FBrisk easterly winds with gales along
OL,16,Fsome southern and western coasts. Hot
OL,17,Fagain in southwest England and Wales.
